  "text": "Successfully completed systematic update of all monorepo packages to use the two-step ESM build process:\n\n1. **compiler**: Converted to pure ESM, updated build scripts, removed tsup dependency\n2. **linter**: Converted to pure ESM, updated build scripts, removed tsup dependency  \n3. **parser**: Converted to pure ESM, updated build scripts, removed tsup dependency\n4. **plugin-cursor**: Converted to pure ESM, updated build scripts, created src/index.ts, removed tsup dependency\n5. **testing**: Converted to pure ESM, updated build scripts, created src/index.ts, removed tsup dependency\n6. **core**: Converted to pure ESM, updated build scripts, cleaned up tsconfig.build.json and tsup.config.ts, removed tsup dependency, fixed path imports\n7. **CLI app**: Converted to pure ESM, updated build scripts, created src/index.ts, made executable, removed eslint/tsup dependencies\n\n- `\"build\": \"rm -rf dist && bun build src/index.ts --outdir dist --target node --minify && tsc --declaration --emitDeclarationOnly --outDir dist --skipLibCheck src/index.ts\"`\n- `\"dev\": \"bun build src/index.ts --outdir dist --target node --watch & tsc --declaration --emitDeclarationOnly --outDir dist --skipLibCheck --watch src/index.ts\"`\n- Pure ESM exports: `{\"types\": \"./dist/index.d.ts\", \"import\": \"./dist/index.js\"}`\n- Added `\"type\": \"module\"` to all packages\n- Added Biome to devDependencies, removed tsup\n\n- Fixed TypeScript spread operator errors in compiler package with proper type casting\n- Fixed CommonJS import issues in core package (path imports changed from default to namespace imports)\n- Created placeholder implementations for missing packages (plugin-cursor, testing)\n- Created basic CLI implementation with Commander.js\n\nAll packages now build successfully and follow the same standardized pattern. The monorepo build process works without any errors.",
